{"tid":847484,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有一個心理變態老豆，做人無希望（長文慎入）","createTime":"2018-10-04T08:03:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T13:15:53.000Z","uid":157321,"like":28,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1a373767d76808d30b6cbfb860d6c566938b2105","tid":847484,"uid":157321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:03:26.000Z","msg":"小弟屋企有一個賤格老豆<br />\n佢唔係個隻包二奶、去爛賭既人<br />\n係個隻恃住自己當年樓價低買咗層樓<br />\n成日屋企佢威作福<br />\n屋企所有人都每分每秒比佢壓迫<br />\n例如佢有唔順眼就又打又鬧<br />\n忍聲吞氣之後<br />\n仲好自鳴得意咁走黎講「同我鬥，無好下場」<br />\n試過衝去想報警<br />\n每次啊媽都喊曬口話報警就會搞到頭家散<br />\n第日無屋企住<br />\n可能你話可以申請公屋、搵社署幫手<br />\n但係香港咩情況大家都知<br />\n正常人根本買唔到樓<br />\n出去租啊媽打工份糧比左粗仲有咩剩<br />\n我同細佬讀緊書<br />\n就算翻part-time 都幫唔到幾多<br />\n真係好辛苦<br />\n屋企有個變態老豆<br />\n佢可以會對住自己屋企人奸笑話無左自己唔得<br />\n見你平日無事都走去撩你<br />\n「點呀 唔鐘意我呀？但你無辦法啵 哈哈哈」<br />\n成個環境同睇宮鬥劇個d有權有勢妃子一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我媽成日好似個傻婆咁匿埋喊<br />\n我究竟做到咩....<br />\n細個同我傾計既人都話 大家努力讀書搵錢 就帶埋媽咪走<br />\n我真係信咗....<br />\n到宜家考到大學...我發現我做唔到<br />\n香港成個社會無辦法令我脫離呢個變態屋企<br />\n見住啊媽成日喊<br />\n話報警搵社工又唔肯<br />\n早幾日又喊<br />\n我淨係識抱著佢<br />\n偷偷流眼淚<br />\n咩都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係好無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n......<br />\n多謝各位巴絲肯曬時間睇我廢up<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3770dac2e9fcf6c6d8f461091c1ab66386131fb7","tid":847484,"uid":36372,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:04:27.000Z","msg":"揾劉江做依個角色"},{"pid":"8abf7a918cc8702be3e3fb0ec49e4bd5f7c7c0be","tid":847484,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:04:52.000Z","msg":"離婚囉搵社工然後申請公屋囉"},{"pid":"0b5a5fe646780fad3a93e5c70dab14ffb57827a0","tid":847484,"uid":9103,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:05:46.000Z","msg":"頭家散又點，咁係你媽媽心目中既家咩？<br />\n同你呀媽講頭家唔散你地個人散，勸下佢搵社工好過啦"},{"pid":"0b52fad33da47a9ddfec1cdf51a6b6d661e79d90","tid":847484,"uid":192748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:05:53.000Z","msg":"離婚啦屌"},{"pid":"8da907d5c79ec278aaf812e622c097b6b2dd6f36","tid":847484,"uid":157321,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8abf7a918cc8702be3e3fb0ec49e4bd5f7c7c0be","tid":847484,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:04:52.000Z","msg":"離婚囉搵社工然後申請公屋囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:06:02.000Z","msg":"我媽唔肯 佢好怕事 我個日拎電話報警佢就成個跪係到求我唔好"},{"pid":"b76f49bf7d9bcf898950cd31633d2db77ab15fb0","tid":847484,"uid":157321,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0b5a5fe646780fad3a93e5c70dab14ffb57827a0","tid":847484,"uid":9103,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:05:46.000Z","msg":"頭家散又點，咁係你媽媽心目中既家咩？<br />\n同你呀媽講頭家唔散你地個人散，勸下佢搵社工好過啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:07:13.000Z","msg":"我同你一樣 我試過咁做 佢就話咁做既話 唔認我做仔...佢係好傳統個種女人觀念 頭家散就乜都無"},{"pid":"dc389c8012aa86e6abe3609c1b3b1ff922a50e24","tid":847484,"uid":124584,"like":10,