g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n......<br />\n多謝各位巴絲肯曬時間睇我廢up<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:16:20.000Z","msg":"some days later. 你仍然壯年，佢就那邊近。 後生的人最後會勝利。"},{"pid":"17bbcd013fc5f77276f0aa9d8a313aec2eaa7e4d","tid":847484,"uid":179775,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b261b6f3e598be4776368cb6acaefcdc75482f60","tid":847484,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:16:03.000Z","msg":"拍片+努力讀好書....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點都忍忍到自己經驗可以獨立"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:17:13.000Z","msg":"完成後撩佢出手.....<br />\n<br />\n一出手報警家暴再離婚<br />\n分完佢錢重可以遠離佢"},{"pid":"20a19f9a145bd6500847ca9c6eadff1a2b4e3cb0","tid":847484,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:19:31.000Z","msg":"拍面證據報警分身家,賣一半樓都夠你租+學費到自力更新.<br />\n<br />\n驚就輸一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d282f082b0741e2ad3a098393ea2a37857d913cd","tid":847484,"uid":81340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:21:27.000Z","msg":"令佢消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a661e0350ea2c60c0f170242a40133f543990f55","tid":847484,"uid":83594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:21:52.000Z","msg":"報警搵社工 唔肯 咁你地繼續受啦<br />\n有個變態老豆係好慘 但係你有之餘，仲要有個怕事阿媽 累埋仔女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e70ea0916ed2e9b0ddca2d066d088d2908a122","tid":847484,"uid":95,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:22:34.000Z","msg":"家暴呢啲你報左警自然有社工同社會褔利署跟進，分分鐘好快派間公屋俾你"},{"pid":"fc72c703805a62cd9b46ff05b6256e6b3dc138e9","tid":847484,"uid":30601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a661e0350ea2c60c0f170242a40133f543990f55","tid":847484,"uid":83594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:21:52.000Z","msg":"報警搵社工 唔肯 咁你地繼續受啦<br />\n有個變態老豆係好慘 但係你有之餘，仲要有個怕事阿媽 累埋仔女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:23:39.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n我係你就自己走算"},{"pid":"78626dbb7a82ba47f7b6886cd17970cc4ca482d9","tid":847484,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:24:40.000Z","msg":"上面講得啱，佢一郁手就拍片報警離婚分佢身家。仲洗做佢奴隸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f8e12480cc95bf843c9b531c5575c0425e2139","tid":847484,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:25:03.000Z","msg":"唔好理阿媽反對 直接搵社工"},{"pid":"0bfb46ac47976de029fb1f87ad76f2bd3c38d49b","tid":847484,"uid":95,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fc72c703805a62cd9b46ff05b6256e6b3dc138e9","tid":847484,"uid":30601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a661e0350ea2c60c0f170242a40133f543990f55","tid":847484,"uid":83594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:21:52.000Z","msg":"報警搵社工 唔肯 咁你地繼續受啦<br />\n有個變態老豆係好慘 但係你有之餘，仲要有個怕事阿媽 累埋仔女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:23:39.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n我係你就自己走算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:25:51.000Z","msg":"係，佢作為呀媽係有責任要保護仔女。勉強維持住呢頭「家」都係無意思。"},{"pid":"435f5cae9ccee0314c92b41170b44f4ed13fd946","tid":847484,"uid":77184,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:27:22.000Z","msg":"啲大陸婆明明屋企冇事都走去扮家暴，搵社署分多間公屋，你呢啲真係屋企有問題，就唔去利用呢啲資源<br />\n<br />\n現實啲，你而家唯一可以做而又可行嘅方法，就係勸你阿媽搵社工跟進<br />\n<br />\n又或者同你阿媽講，如果佢再唔肯搵社工，你就去帶細佬一齊申請政府嗰啲青年宿舍，到時頭家一樣會散，問吓佢想跟你老竇定跟你兩兄弟囉"},{"pid":"1e9648188840586c528676b230d08cc8ca11fcc4","tid":847484,"uid":44277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:27:27.000Z","msg":"差唔多，到我反抗嗰陣我媽鬧返我轉頭<br />\n所以而家嫁咗人乜7都唔理，唔好剩係諗到老豆有問題，根本呀媽都有問題"},{"pid":"354975f38df442f9a4718d2936cffabb2883f4f4","tid":847484,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:29:03.000Z","msg":"有個狂燥老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同佢一d都唔熟，想讀好d書做野<br />\n脫離佢，建立自己未曾擁有嘅幸福家庭<br />\n<br />\n宜家唔會主動同佢講野，佢聊我講都只係:嗯哦好"},{"pid":"0f2aa4d2e49384d09e6b3f38731e07ae7c17ae8d","tid":847484,"uid":78755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8da907d5c79ec278aaf812e622c097b6b2dd6f36","tid":847484,"uid":157321,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8abf7a918cc8702be3e3fb0ec49e4bd5f7c7c0be","tid":847484,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:04:52.000Z","msg":"離婚囉搵社工然後申請公屋囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:06:02.000Z","msg":"我媽唔肯 佢好怕事 我個日拎電話報警佢就成個跪係到求我唔好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:30:37.000Z","msg":"咁繼續受 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa001126466e7410c30c0f581bcd4abbdbf4f1e","tid":847484,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:38:21.000Z","msg":"教下你老豆咩叫風水輪流轉。<br />\n<br />\n同佢講係咪想你老個陣掉你去老人院，等你自生自滅，孤獨死，然後死個陣冇人送你終? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(除非你老豆同你阿媽離婚再係出面再娶過第二件生仔，但係你同阿媽就可以分佢家產。)"}]}